                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.95
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Samples of curium consisting",
                "mostly of Cm244 (95%) and containing smaller quantities",
                " of heavier curium isotopes."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CHSEP",
                "REC",
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The product nuclei recoiling from",
                "the target were collected on thin gold foils. These",
                "foils were dissolved and the bulk of the fission-",
                "product and induced activity was removed by a",
                "combination of solvent-extraction and ion-exchange",
                "techniques. The actinide fraction could then be",
                "examined immediately in the alpha pulse-height",
                "analyzer."
              ]
            }
          ],
